                            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

                            <h4>At Pelican Roofing Group, your privacy matters to us. We are committed to respecting and protecting your privacy and any personal information you provide to us or we collect.</h4>

                            <h4>This privacy policy should be understood as our Terms of Use, and describes our privacy practices. We will notify you of the following:</h4>
                            
